Unescaped strings:

    @"x\z"  -->  "x\\z"



Rich strings:

    $"xyz"  -->  "<html>xyz</html>"



Unescaped rich strings:

    @$"x\z"  -->  "<html>x\\z</html>"



Literal concats:

    "x" "yz"  -->  "xyz"
    "x""yz"   -->  "x\"yz"



++ strings:

    ++"xyz"  -->  "\nxyz"
    "xyz"++  -->  "xyz\n"
    ++ may be added any number of times.


